{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9cf91b4105","title":"中央文革关于银川新华社事件的指示","origin":"原载宁夏无产阶级革命派总指挥部政治部等编 《宁夏回族自治区无产阶级文化大革命（文件汇编）》，1968年1月27日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e73c319ef6","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"9cf91b4105"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e208109710","name":"宁夏文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1d02c8ce81","type":"title","text":"中央文革关于银川新华社事件的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105"},{"id":"343dbf816b","type":"appellation","text":"宁夏自治区军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105"},{"id":"eea5ddd86f","type":"paragraph","text":"五月卅日在银川发生的捣毁宁夏新华分社、抢劫新华分社的机密文件和其他物资，并殴打新华社记者的事件，是一个严重点政治事件。宁夏自治区军区有责任保护新华分社的正常工作和记者的人身安全。为此，责成宁夏军区负责处理这一事件：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105"},{"id":"a9e7a1b2ec","type":"paragraph","text":"1.把这次闹事的头头抓起来，审查处理。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105"},{"id":"97231767e5","type":"paragraph","text":"2.把抢走的全部文件和物资负责追回。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105"},{"id":"d993e7354f","type":"paragraph","text":"3.由军区负责把这一事件调查清楚，依法论处。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105"},{"id":"af5203e3b7","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央文革小组办事组一九六七年六月六日","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105"}],"page":{"id":"f2d46f6b7b","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9cf91b4105","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}